      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FRACTIOUS FABIAN (1) turned in a better run last time to find a minor placing (18.34) at this track behind Saint Ella in a Maiden. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. One of the contenders. CADILLAC EXPRESS (7) copped a check in the run and finished a well held 9 lengths third (18.61) last time in a Maiden at this track over 305m. Solid beginner and with a good start should have clear running out wide. Harder here but expected to measure up. MY BOO BOO (2) makes her debut without a trial but profiles well for first outing. Expected to play a major role. FABULOUS FLOYD (4) was out of the money here on debut but expected to be much improved.",
